-- Troika Hires Dirk Werner, Angelo Morganti for Investment Banking
-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 2012-02-29T07:02:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-29/troika-hires-dirk-werner-angelo-morganti-for-investment-banking.html
Troika Dialog, the Russian brokerage
acquired last year by OAO Sberbank, hired Dirk Werner and Angelo
Morganti as managing directors of its  investment banking 
division.  Morganti was hired from  Renaissance Capital  while Werner
has worked for companies including Bank of America Merrill
Lynch,  Morgan Stanley (MS)  and  Lehman Brothers , Troika said in a
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason Corcoran in Moscow at 
 jcorcoran13@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Brad Cook at 
